commit 08733a2228ac4b2739355b536adf955d982a40f0
Author: Carl Worth <cworth@cworth.org>
Date:	Wed Apr 26 21:22:58 2006 -0700

    Move 1.4 schedule up. Add more bugs from sunmoon1997

    To hit the Firefox 3 schedule in early 2007 we'll need to have a
    1.4 release
    out much sooner. Let's shoot for October 2006 which gives 6 months
    between
    1.2 and 1.4.

    Also, sunmoon1997 has identified a couple more important issues to
    be fixed
    before 1.2 releases.

