commit 7110c168f7edadcedaea74a73b7ac6f095165931
Author: Carl Worth <cworth@cworth.org>
Date:	Wed Apr 26 12:36:22 2006 -0700

    Remove redeundant -rgb24-ref.png images.

    In several cases the -rgb24 reference images were identical to the
    -ref images.
    So we change the logic to find the latter if the former doesn't exist,
    and then
    we remove the redundant images.

