Date:	Mon Nov 21 10:50:20 2005 +0000

    Add reminder to fix all memory leaks (as determined by the test suite)
    before release 1.2.0.
    Patch leak of patterns as noted in bug #5100 (thanks to Richard
    Stellingwerff <remenic@gmail.com>).

