    Pass a format to the surface create functions. (create_image_surface):
    Condense create_argb_image_surface and create_rgb_image_surface
    into a single function. (create_xlib_surface): Add support for
    CAIRO_FORMAT_RGB24 in addition to CAIRO_FORMAT_ARGB32. Add a new
    target for testing xlib with CAIRO_FORMAT_RGB24.

