commit 999c2a8a2b27412ac2fb59041837c780e6d7eec3
Author: Carl Worth <cworth@cworth.org>
Date:	Mon Sep 12 11:15:52 2005 +0000

    Originally 2005-09-06 Carl Worth <cworth@cworth.org>:
    _cairo_cache_preserve -> _cairo_cache_freeze _cairo_cache_release ->
    _cairo_cache_thaw
    Track rename of _cairo_cache_freeze/thaw.
    Track rename. Add stacking behavior to
    _cairo_cache_freeze/thaw. Abstract out shrinking from
    _cairo_cache_insert so that _cairo_cache_thaw will also shrink
    as necessary.
    Make this function static since its current limitation to accept an
    entry rather than a key makes it not as externally useful as would
    be desirable. Document this limitation.

